dosd - dmenu-style osd
======================
dosd is an OSD tool for X11 in the style of dmenu


Requirements
------------
In order to build dosd you need the Xlib and Freetype header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dosd is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dosd
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running dosd
------------
See the man page for details.
